Recommends: postfix, dovecot-imapd, mariadb-client
Description: typed Python CLI + daemon for PostfixAdmin-schema mail servers
 il-postino administers domains, mailboxes, aliases, alias-domains, and
 mlmmj mailing lists on a Postfix + Dovecot stack using the PostfixAdmin
 SQL schema. Includes:
  * postino(1)   - operator CLI (typed, pyright-strict, audit-logged)
  * postinod(8)  - HTTP daemon (SCIM 2.0 + Zitadel event sink)
 .
 The whole Python venv is bundled in /usr/share/postino/venv so no pip
 install runs at package-install time. Closed-world, no internet
 required to install.
